    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直面绑架的恐惧，以及你内心深处的惊悚。  <br><br>来自 《破碎怪谈》 系列的 《无光破晓》，这是一款第一人称生存恐怖游戏，在其中现实破碎为偏执、绝望与噩梦般的幻象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/2275d997ac3da484949c9520bb1756ef.poster.avif?t=1759630374\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/2275d997ac3da484949c9520bb1756ef.webm?t=1759630374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/2275d997ac3da484949c9520bb1756ef.mp4?t=1759630374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演一名绑架受害者，被迫面对人类能想象到的最黑暗罪行：人口贩卖、器官买卖，以及暗网中潜藏的恐怖。  <br>但活下去并逃离绑匪仅仅是开始，你那脆弱的心灵才可能是最致命的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⏳ 时间与你为敌</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的生物钟决定事件何时发生。休息过久，死亡可能在睡梦中降临；行动过早，则可能准备不足。每一个决定都至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/8eaed59a9b4fa70a1440035364c472fc.poster.avif?t=1759630374\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/8eaed59a9b4fa70a1440035364c472fc.webm?t=1759630374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/8eaed59a9b4fa70a1440035364c472fc.mp4?t=1759630374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🛠️ 创造以求生</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集并制造工具以提高生存几率。每一种资源都很重要，而每一个错误都可能致命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/9c5554cd9ca5ec5ccea4aca6401673a7.poster.avif?t=1759630374\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/9c5554cd9ca5ec5ccea4aca6401673a7.webm?t=1759630374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/9c5554cd9ca5ec5ccea4aca6401673a7.mp4?t=1759630374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >👁️ 心灵是牢笼</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强效镇静剂会将你拖入幻觉，把熟悉的事物扭曲成怪诞。上一刻你还在满是毛绒玩具的玩具店，下一刻却置身于猛兽潜伏的草原。  <br>逃离自己的心灵将是你面临的最大挑战之一。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/8a23095a3056e70b730d029642af4361.poster.avif?t=1759630374\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/8a23095a3056e70b730d029642af4361.webm?t=1759630374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/8a23095a3056e70b730d029642af4361.mp4?t=1759630374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🕯️ 绝望吞噬你</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忽视心理健康，恐慌便会掌控一切。进入「抑郁模式」后，黑暗实体会无情地追捕你，吞噬你的绝望，直到一切化为虚无。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/f60025682255f93c336d717465059e66.poster.avif?t=1759630374\" width=780 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/f60025682255f93c336d717465059e66.webm?t=1759630374\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283250/extras/f60025682255f93c336d717465059e66.mp4?t=1759630374\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >...一次 破碎怪谈 体验...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《无光破晓》将恐怖推进至禁忌领域。没有安全之地，没有稳定依靠，只有选择、谎言，以及每条道路都可能通往毁灭的恐惧。</p>",
